name: Friends In Deed Non-Profit Organization
review_text: This is a place where families and low income people can get a week's worth of groceries for free. The food is delicious and nourishing plus the pride in being able to put food on the table and your children will always have something healthy to snack on between meals. Tuesdays, Wednesdays, and Thursdays starting after 12pm. Check their front door for hours, and there is a sign up paper to keep your place in line. Documents needed will be told to you on your first visit. Identification for everyone in your household, and proof of income.
